<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨٤-<span class="c5"> وَأَخْبَرَنِي عَبْدُ الْمَلِكِ قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ يَقُولُ: نَاظَرَنِي إِنْسَانٌ مَرَّةً -<span class="c5"> وَأَظُنُّهُ قَالَ:</span> من مِنْ أَهْلِ الْمَدِينَةِ قَالَ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">لَيْسَ هِيَ:</span> <span class="c2">((أَحِفُّوا الشَّوَارِبَ)</span>) .<span class="c5"> إِنَّمَا هِيَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">((حُفُّوا)</span>) بِغَيْرِ أَلِفٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> فَنَظَرْتُ فِي كِتَابِي فَإِذَا هِيَ فِي مَوْضِعَيْنِ أَلِفٌ مُثْبَتَةٌ <span class="c2">((أَحِفُّوا)</span>) .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>